item.description:
Hi Trailblazers, join us for an evening of socializing and dancing! We will meet at TJ's in Portsmouth they have a private room for us with a bar.

Around 9:30 we will go dancing at one of the various dancing nightclubs in the downtown Portsmouth area.

We will be joined by other meetup groups!

If anyone gets lost or wants more info: call me at: 603-312-6735

See you there!

Peter
item.why: Meet at DJ and after this we will go dancing
